OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAlmost a quarter of kids   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faged 5-7 have smartphones  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nearly a quarter of UK                 
OL,6, five-to-seven-year-olds now have their 
OL,7, own smartphone, Ofcom research         
OL,8, suggests.                              
OL,10,FSocial media use also rose in the age  
OL,11,Fgroup over last year with nearly two in
OL,12,Ffive using messaging service WhatsApp, 
OL,13,Fdespite its minimum age of 13.         
OL,15,FThe communications regulator warned    
OL,16,Fparental enforcement of rules "appeared
OL,17,Fto be diminishing."                    
OL,19,FIt also said the figures should be a   
OL,20,F"wake up call" for the industry to do  
OL,21,Fmore to protect children.              
